text: 162 (one hundred sixty-two) is a number. It comes after 161 and before 163. == In mathematics == 162 is a composite number, because it can be made by multiplying other numbers together. Its prime factorization is: 162 = 2 × 3⁴ == In sports == In Major League Baseball, each team normally plays 162 games in the regular season. Category:Integers
title: 162 (number)
